sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Admin
    participant B as Browser
    participant W as WebThaoCamVien (AdminController)
    participant DB as WebContext (SQL Server)

    U->>B: Mo /Admin/Heatmap
    B->>W: GET /Admin/Heatmap?from&to&poiId

    Note over W: AuthN/AuthZ (cookie) + validate range

    W->>DB: Aggregate visits/playback by POI (time bucket)
    DB-->>W: points(lat,lng,intensity) + legend

    W-->>B: 200 View(HeatmapViewModel)
    B-->>U: Render heatmap layer + legend

    opt Doi filter/range
        U->>B: Chon range moi / chon POI
        B->>W: GET /Admin/Heatmap?from&to&poiId
        W->>DB: Re-aggregate
        DB-->>W: points + legend
        W-->>B: 200 View/Partial/JSON
        B-->>U: Update heatmap
    end
